ğŸ“ Summary & Why This Matters
âœ… NO need to build a complex Docker Compose setup
âœ… This method is simpler and beginner-friendly
âœ… Works on Windows with Docker Desktop
âœ… Helps integrate open-source tools like Open WebUI + SearXNG effectively

